      "widgets_values": [
        "A magical and heartwarming animation set in a whimsical fairy-tale meadow with a charming mushroom house. The scene begins with a peaceful, sunlit view of the mushroom house, surrounded by colorful flowers and lush green grass. The camera slowly zooms in toward the house, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere.\n\nAs the animation progresses, the round wooden door gently creaks open, revealing a pair of glowing eyes peeking out. Slowly, an adorable 3D cartoon bunny with big, sparkling eyes and fluffy fur steps out, looking around curiously. The bunny takes a small hop forward, its ears twitching and its nose wiggling as it happily greets the world outside. The soft sunlight highlights the bunny’s fur, making it look extra cuddly and warm.\n\nThe animation is smooth and expressive, capturing the bunny’s subtle movements—blinking, ear twitches, and a gentle head tilt—adding to the magical and wholesome feel of the scene. The background remains dreamy and softly blurred, enhancing the enchanting fairy-tale setting.\n"
